caption: Nice semi-hidden spot near Grand Lake theater. Tasty sandwiches for a reasonable price.
One of the best sandwich shops I've ever been to. Everything I've tried off the menu is delicious, and everyone I've taken here agrees. The owner is also super friendly and helpful. Highly recommend.
Enchanting. Magnanimous. Beyond every idea of delicious.
Meatball samwich was really tasty

"Dear God, the bread is turning translucent."  I whispered this to myself, as I patiently reheated the pulled pork sandwich I'd gotten yesterday from Modigliani Cafe.  This place is truly one-of-a-kind. It's a tight menu, but behind every …

Great local place for a sandwich. I would recommend the Cuban sandwich.  Dropping my review because I was ignored by the cashier. I don’t mind waiting, but it felt cold to ignore me, walk past me, and check up on someone who ordered after me only for the busy cook to notice I haven’t received my order.
I'd love to try something else but the Cuban is so good I get it every time. For $10 including tax? Hard to beat. (Cash only.)
Tasty meatball sub!

We had such a wonderful experience at Modigliani Cafe yesterday.  The owner hooked us up with a bunch of samples upon arrival and was just so kind and friendly.  The pork was incredible and he had two amazing sandwiches (Cuban and Turkey).  Highly recommend!!
Classic spot. Great sandwiches! Turkey with pepper jam or the meatball are my fav.

An Oakland gem. The sandwiches are delicious as he makes everything in house. And the prices are ridiculous especially for what you get. not just one of the best sandwich shops but just one of the best places to eat in the East Bay.
Greek salad was delicious!
Best veggie sandwich I have ever had!

Things are not the same anymore.  I dont know what happened but the Cuban sandwich just did not hit the spot like it did before.  I go back to try it again, and as I am waiting patiently, the older gentleman looks at me and doesnt …

This place is actually a 4.5 star rating just so we're clear, but I'm happy to round up to a 5 because of the wonderful service.  Inside is simple, with the menu right up front, super easy to read. The guys working there were very nice, and …
Super friendly staff. The sandwiches are filling and delicious!
Amazing in house made meats. Everything I got to sample before I even got my sandwich was tasty and fresh.
One of the best sandwiches I've ever had
More of a take-out place than a cafe. Tasty sandwiches. Be ready to wait 20 minutes while they are prepared.

Delicious panini sandwiches made with love. Jerry, the owner, is an absolute delight. The sandwiches take some time to make, but the ingredients are fresh and it’s worth the wait. Highly recommend this spot!
I don’t know why this place isn’t talked about more! The service is awesome and the paninis are outstanding. The price is right too!
Everything is made from scratch, this place is absolutely delicious
Very helpful and great at his craft don't sleep on this place folks
Best paninis in Bay. Generous portions. The meat/bread ratio is on point. The owner is very friendly and accommodating. Everything is house-made. Try the secret hot sauce that's made by the owner.

I had been having the WORST day, and I was hangry to the max. So, my fiancé googled “sandwiches” & headed straight to Modigliani. He came home with the BEST tuna sandwich I’ve ever had & I am so dang thankful For him & you’re wonderful sandwich maker ❤️
Great food, great service. Recommended place .
They have yummy panini sandwiches...

Can’t believe I didn’t find this place sooner!  Excellent panini style sandwiches with high quality homemade ingredients. The owner is super friendly and really makes the whole experience feel special.  FYI it’s cash only but they have an ATM inside
Nice employees, big and filling sandwiches. Some outdoor seating and inside bar setup seating. Sodas, water and patatoe chips available for purchase

The pics from everyone drew me in and they don't lie the sammies are generous and delicious. Bread is fresh and toasted perfectly. The owner was super welcoming. I had my ❤️ set on a steak sandwich but next time I'm going to be trying the …
Well crafted delicious sandwiches and friendly service make this place a welcome addition to the neighborhood.  They make a mean Cubano with tasty roast pork and ham 😋
Really friendly people and great hearty sandwiches. Will be back!
Amazing food and incredible service! The owner could not be kinder :)
The steak panini was excellent! Wonderful service.
It was a pretty good sandwich, but not dying to go back.
Best Panini in Oakland
Amazing pulled pork. Got a taste test as it came out of the oven. Delicious, delicious, delicious..
Rude customer service & employees. Don’t waste your time.
This place has an unassuming storefront with top notch sandwiches (panini) and shakes. A must try! It's delicious!
Most reasonably priced place in the Bay, 6-star customer service and delicious to boot. Highly recommended.
Great Sandwiches!!! Great prices!!! Great service!!!
The Cuban sandwich here is one of the best sandwiches I’ve had, period. Everything I’ve had here is great and affordable. Total gem
The veggie panini was incredible!

Super friendly and personable owner! A really great experience eating lunch here. Everything is made in house (including the hot sauce!) and super delicious. Portions are large and prices are very reasonable.
Try Veggie panini here. Owner is friendly too 😊

Literally just happened to walk by on way to another establishment. Ordered the Cuban, they nailed it. The pork, with ham, cheese mustard and pickles with the bread perfectly grilled. Everything is made on site. Must try spot, in fact going again for lunch today!
Best meatball sandwich!

I’ve passed by this place for years without trying it and wow, have I been missing out! This is a fantastic sandwich and salad spot. Really delicious, fresh and well made food. They clearly care about their craft. Forget Whole Foods or even Bi-Rite deli sandwiches. This place has some of the best I’ve had on either side of the bay!
Great Sammie's...long wait time
Goo quality sandwiches. Would recommend the Cuban.
Really nice people, great sandwiches every time and interesting salads.
This place is fantastic! really nice folks to run it. a lot of homemade stuff. really fantastic

Phenomenal food --  really most excellent. i have been coming here for a couple of years the food is incredibly fresh and prepared with care. What sets this place apart is that everything is made with love and it really shows.

Honestly. Just wow. The kind of place you hear about from your grandfather and spend your whole life searching for. Sandwiches so big you need to unbutton your pants when you walk out. Personal favorites are tuna melt (ordinarily I don't …
One of the best Oakland sandwhich shops around! Really great food and service, try turkey sandwhich it’s delicious
Great salads and sandwiches at a great price. Veggie panino is top-notch. Cash only.
Amazing. Enormous. And the milkshakes ❤️
Farro, tomatoes and cucumber salad was amazing. It was not only reasonably priced and healthy but also delicious. Would definitely recommend.
Best large sandwiches. 1 is easily shareable for two people.
Had the meatball, great. Had the Cuban, great.
Delicious sandwiches with huge portions
Terrific sandwiches!
One of the best places to get a tasty sandwich

You walk close by and you wonder where is that awesome smell coming from. It's this little gem. Great food really. My husband and I tried the meatball sub and the cuban sandwich here and it was awesome. Lovely taste and great value. Will be back!
The best grilled sandwich in the the bay area!
These are the best sandwiches by far. Old fashioned recipes prepared with great dedication.
Amazing customer service and delicious sandwichs!
Pulled Pork Amazing Delicious Great Place

This is an AWESOME  place to eat. Everywhere we travel I always order a veggie meal and my companion is always looking for a Cuban sandwich (he's from FL).  I ordered the Veggie Panini with the perfect combination of grilled eggplant, …
Great sandwiches,  downside is that they add way too much meat in their sandwiches. Their customer service is great as well. I will be back soon!

I came this place all the time. Whenecer there friends visit Oakland I always take them here for a quick lunch when we walk by the lake. This is the one of best top 3 sandwich place in Oakland. Cash only. Pulled prok and Cuban are to die for!

My wife and I dropped in on a rainy afternoon and were truly surprised and delighted. We had a meatball and a sausage sandwich. I am considered a very good cook by many, and I must say, I could hardly do a better job then they do. …

Went in by accident,  the yuppie place we were going to had a 30 minute wait. It's a little hole in the wall but the menu looked good. I had a cuban sandwich and it was so delicious!!! It was so stocked full of delicious meat and tasty …
Best sandwiches ever. I had the turkey panini with brie and pepper jam. If this place was in SF, there would be a line out the door. Go eat here people! Soon!
This place is amazing. Have not had a meal that I didn't absolutely love. The pulled pork is a winner, as well the cucumber salad is awesome.
Best sandwich place by far!! Friendly people, great milkshakes. Love it!
Hard-to-beat veggie pannino for $8.50 and nice easygoing guys at your service. Ritornerò!
One the best Cuban sandwiches I've had in my life. Crisp/moist bread, high quality meats and real mustard seeds!
The pulled pork panini was super delicious!!

Super friendly, family owned, local sandwich spot. I love coming in here and chatting with the owners while chowing down on one of their awesome cuban sandwiches. If you are in the area be sure to give it a try, just be sure to have cash (they don't accept credit cards at the moment).
